transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan ji madam. Hello haan, haan Jahangir sir very good morning sir, Rani baat kar rahi thi IndiaMART se.
Customer: Haan ji madam ji.
Executive: A haan ji haan ji sir kaise hain aap?
Customer: Bas shukr Allah ka.
Executive: Haan ji sir. Sir abhi dekhiye sir abhi start hua kya? Ek baar application ek baar open karte hain na?
Customer: Nahi chal raha hai wahi same hi hai.
Executive: Nahi chal raha hai sir same issue aa raha hai?
Customer: Same issue wahi hai.
Executive: Sir ek baar dekhiye ek baar open karke dekhiye. Kyunki maine
Customer: Accha.
Executive: Maine abhi check kiya hai nahi chal raha hai.
Executive: Same issue hai nahi chal raha hai.
Customer: Nahi chal raha hai.
Executive: Sir ek baar abhi aaj ka aap mere ko screenshot share karenge kya?
Customer: Wahi same hai same hai.
Executive: Ek baar screenshot mere ko share kijiye haan.
Customer: Same wahi issue hai.
Executive: Ek baar aap screenshot mere ko share kijiye.
Customer: Ye khali mujhe ho raha hai ya ki kisi aur ko bhi aisa hi hai?
Executive: Nahi aur matlab sabko nahi ho raha but haan ek do customer ko ho raha hai sir. To internal na humne wo kar diya hai technical team ko, thik hai? Mujhe bhi mujhe kal banda hai bola tha usko bhi aise hi problem hai.
Executive: Haan haan wahi main keh rahi hoon.
Executive: Aap mere ko screenshot share kijiye phir se sir.
Customer: Ek second bhej raha hoon. Haan haan.
Customer: Leads to aa rahe hai valid leads aa rahe hai magar consume nahi ho raha hai.
Executive: Valid leads aa rahe hai dikh rahe hai aapko?
Customer: Haan aa rahe hai na upar dikh raha hai screen pe aa raha hai.
Executive: To abhi waha pe consume matlab contact bar now ka option to aa raha hoga?
Customer: Wo to aa raha hai wo to hum jab open kar rahe hai to nahi ho raha hai.
Customer: Same yahi issue jo maine aapko whatsapp pe bheja hai.
Executive: Ek second. Ek minute na.
Executive: Same issue aa raha hai na? Waha pe aapko waha pe by list dikh raha hai waha pe but yaha pe kuch option hi nahi aa raha hai. Thik hai?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai sir main isko main dikha karwati hoon, thik hai?
Customer: Thik hai okay.
